name: Let me do it for you
description: Inspired by the globally viral TikTok meme, $NOSE captures the heart of internet culture and community. At its core, $NOSE represents the iconic "Let me do it for you" meme featuring the lovable borzoi dog with an exceptionally long nose. This meme isn’t just about a quirky image—it embodies a spirit of determination, selflessness, and humor. The borzoi's long nose symbolizes its ability to tackle challenges and "reach" goals that seem impossible, all while bringing a smile to people's faces.
